quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  2,40,"Abange abaana ba Israel, mujjukire (mwebaze) ebyengera byange bye nabagabira. Mutuukirize e ndagaano yange (ey'okunzikiriza n'okugondera amateeka gange), nja kutuukiriza e ndagaano yammwe (ey'okubayingiza e jjana). Era nze nzekka gwe muba mutya"
  2,41,"Era mukkirize ebyo bye nassa (ku Nabbi Muhammad) nga bikakasa ebyo bye mulina (Taurat) era temuba abasaale mu kubiwakanya. Era temutundanga ebigambo byange omuwendo omutono (olw’emigaso gy'ensi), era mutye nze nzekka"
  2,42,"Temutabulanga amazima n'ebitali bituufu, ne mukisa amazima nga mumanyi"
  2,43,"Muyimirizeewo e sswala, mutoole zzaka, era mukutame n'abo abakutama"
  2,44,"Mulagira mutya abantu okukola obulungi ne mwerabira emyoyo gyammwe, so nga ate mmwe musoma e kitabo (Taurat), abange temutegeera"
  2,45,"Mweyambise obugumiikiriza n'okusaala, wabula yo e sswala ekaluubirira nnyo abantu, okugyako abo abagondera Katonda"
  2,46,"Abo abakakasa nti bakusisinkana Omulezi waabwe (Katonda), era gyali gye bagenda okudda"